name: Baruak Series 01/06
description:
Baruak is the second character created by Ilham Afrora (Illousa Sajaklamo) after Pandora. 
Baruak means monkey, Baruak is the Minangkabau language (West Sumatra), Indonesia.
Baruak 01 is a baruak who has a confident expression of good character, and is hardworking
